ata, revealed the same dependency of amyloidogenicity,\nsuggesting the importance of {\\alpha}-helical structure as opposed to sequence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 3 Dec 2017 18:43:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-22"}
